## Test ID Conventions

When documenting tests, use prefixes for component/module names:

| Prefix | Component/Module |
|--------|------------------|
| UT | utils |
| API | api handlers |
| SVC | services |
| CMP | components |
| PG | pages |
| HK | hooks |

New components/modules should get a 2-3 letter prefix.

